definition.text: This page serves as a dictionary so you can look up Crypto/Superalgos terms or technical terms. This page simply serves as a dictionary with hopefully good explanations of those technical words.

paragraphs.text: However, do not accidentally confuse this dictionary with the "technical terms" page as the words listed on the "technical terms" page should not be translated into your language.
